Reclusa::

She placed a hand gently on his shoulder and smiled at him. "I thank
you.   Bring what ever you feel is needed to decorate this room
properly. I trust your skills and know that you will do an excellent
job."  Her tone of voice was confident.  Her optics shined at him,
knowing that a spider's gaze can instill different responces. This
gaze was to instill a loyalty responce from him. Though she had no
intentions of taking over, she still wanted a few bots she could count
on to be there for her if needed. "I require rest now. I need to let
my power cells recharge. We can make all the changes later on. I thank
you again."  And with that, she swept into her new room.
